    <task id="LOCAL-00005" summary="Refactored `Packager` to use granular transcoding methods and improved the CLI workflow.&#10;&#10;- Split the monolithic `encode` method into `transcode_video`, `transcode_audio`, and `extract_subtitles`.&#10;- Implemented video transcoding progress tracking by piping `ffmpeg` output.&#10;- Added a `OnceLock` to `Packager` to cache `MediaMetadata`.&#10;- Updated the CLI to manage the full transcode-and-package lifecycle, including temporary file cleanup.&#10;- Introduced `env_logger` for structured logging and added specific `TranscodeError` and `PackagerError` types.&#10;- Fixed duration calculation in metadata extraction.">
