    <task id="LOCAL-00008" summary="Implemented a background media processing service for transcoding and packaging.&#10;&#10;- Introduced `PackagerService` to manage an asynchronous pipeline for transcoding video (720p, 1080p), extracting audio/subtitles, and HLS packaging.&#10;- Implemented `MediaProcessorRepository` to persist media metadata and track processing status in SQLite.&#10;- Added a `/enqueue` POST endpoint to trigger the processing pipeline for specific media files.&#10;- Updated the `Packager` utility to improve `ffmpeg` error handling, capture stdout progress, and return the final master playlist path.&#10;- Enhanced the database migration runner to support multiple SQL statements per migration file.&#10;- Expanded the database schema (Migration v3) to include tables for `metadata`, `chapters`, `streams`, and `processing_queue`.&#10;- Added `uuid` and `directories` dependencies to manage unique processing identifiers and project data paths.">
